---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="About - Tech AI Blog"
  description="Learn about our mission to explore and explain AI and technology"
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-secondary-900 dark:text-white mb-8">About Tech AI Blog</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert">
      <p class="lead text-xl text-secondary-600 dark:text-secondary-400 mb-8">
        We're passionate about making complex technology concepts accessible to everyone.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-800 dark:text-secondary-200 mt-12 mb-4">
        Our Mission
      </h2>
      <p>
        At Tech AI Blog, we believe that understanding artificial intelligence and emerging
        technologies shouldn't be limited to experts. Our mission is to bridge the gap between
        complex technical concepts and practical applications.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-800 dark:text-secondary-200 mt-12 mb-4">
        What We Cover
      </h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning</li>
        <li>Software Development Best Practices</li>
        <li>Emerging Technologies and Trends</li>
        <li>Technical Tutorials and Guides</li>
        <li>Industry Insights and Analysis</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-800 dark:text-secondary-200 mt-12 mb-4">
        Our Values
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-2">
            Accessibility
          </h3>
          <p>Making complex topics understandable for everyone.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-2">
            Accuracy
          </h3>
          <p>Ensuring our content is technically accurate and up-to-date.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-2">
            Practicality
          </h3>
          <p>Focusing on real-world applications and solutions.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-2">
            Community
          </h3>
          <p>Fostering a supportive environment for learning and discussion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
